        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Generic agencies build generic websites. They'll hand you something that could belong to any gym in any city, slap your logo on it, and call it done.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          I focus on gyms and fitness businesses. I know how people decide where to train, what makes them trust a gym before they visit, and what gets them to actually fill out that contact form.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Done in 2–3 weeks, not months</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">You own everything — no monthly ransom fees</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Built for local Google search from day one</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Custom design, not a template your competitor already has</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">I respond when you message me</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <CheckCircle className="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">No confusing contracts or hidden costs</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
